B.UH=new A.K("Introdu\xe7\xe3o","Last updated: July 2026")
B.Uc=new A.K("What is PerfectGest I?","A mobile business management app. Data is stored locally (SQLite). No PerfectGest cloud account for clients, estimates, or cash.")
B.Tb=new A.K("Does it work offline?","Offline-first for daily use. Optional Google services (Analytics, Remote Config, minimal Firestore for subscription eligibility) may need a network when active.")
B.TC=new A.K("Can I use the app without a subscription?","Yes, to explore (browse screens and the interface). Operations (creating clients, commercial or fiscal estimates, cash entries; generating management PDFs; encrypted backup restore; and other gated actions) require Pro Plan. Trying an operation without a subscription shows a notice with the plan (reference R$ 9.90/month; price on Google Play) and Subscribe or Continue exploring app features.")
B.TS=new A.K("How does the Pro Plan work?","Monthly or annual subscription on Google Play: clients, estimates, cash and PDFs without practical limits; encrypted backup restore; interactive business card (vCard, QR, preview). Manage in Settings \u2192 Google Play subscription.")
B.Sc=new A.K("Where do I manage the subscription?","Settings \u2192 Google Play subscription. Cancel via Play Store \u2192 Payments & subscriptions.")
B.Ut=new A.K("What is the Quote/NF-e/NFS-e tab?","A local fiscal quote (products and services, NCM/CFOP/LC 116 codes, support PDF) plus code lookup/registration. It does not issue electronic NF-e/NFS-e to tax authorities.")
B.Tf=new A.K("What is the digital business card?","In Company, edit professional business details only (not clients or cash). Share card generates a PNG via the system share sheet. After your first card, without Pro Plan the card is static (you can still share the snapshot PNG); with Pro, edit and use advanced features in the app only (vCard, QR, interactive preview) \u2014 no PerfectGest-hosted web page.\n\nClients and financial data stay protected on the device and are not sent to servers automatically.")
B.U9=new A.K("Are my client and financial data protected?","Yes. Stored locally (including fiscal quotes). They leave the device only if you share a PDF, card PNG/vCard/QR, or an exported backup file (encrypted backup recommended on Pro).")
B.Uo=new A.K("Fiscal reminders, weekly calendar, Latest entries, notifications, ads, Crashlytics, languages?","On-device fiscal reminders (informational only); weekly calendar in Company; home shortcuts to recent records; local notifications only; no ads; no Crashlytics; PT / EN / ES.")
B.T7=new A.K("Privacy, deletion, suggestions?","Settings \u2192 Help and support for legal links. Wipe device: Settings \u2192 Data on this device \u2192 Delete all data. Feedback: Company tab \u2192 email suporte@perfectgestdev.com.")
B.a_4=s([B.UH,B.Uc,B.Tb,B.TC,B.TS,B.Sc,B.Ut,B.Tf,B.U9,B.Uo,B.T7],t.h)
