B.TB=new A.K("1. Nature of data","PerfectGest-Clinica III may process sensitive personal data (health data) entered by the clinic or professional using the software (e.g. medical records and visit history).")
B.S8=new A.K("2. LGPD roles","\u2022 Controller: clinic or health professional using the software (defines purposes and means of processing).\n\u2022 Software operator: Perfect Gest Dev (PERFECT GEST DESENVOLVIMENTO DE SOFTWARE LTDA).\n\u2022 Sub-processors (when applicable):\n  \u2014 Microsoft (subscription payments via Microsoft Store)\n  \u2014 Meta/WhatsApp (messages, if configured by the clinic)\n  \u2014 Firebase/Google (technical components, if enabled)")
B.RK=new A.K("3. Minimization and storage","\u2022 Clinical data remains on the device (local SQLite).\n\u2022 Audit logs store metadata (who / when / what), without clinical content.")
B.TP=new A.K("4. Data subject rights (LGPD Art. 18)","The app provides operational support for:\n\u2022 access and correction via patient record;\n\u2022 LGPD report export (ADMIN) in PDF/CSV (when available);\n\u2022 portability via encrypted backup.\n\nTo exercise rights regarding health data, contact the clinic first (controller).")
B.Ur=new A.K("5. Recommended security (best practices)","\u2022 Enable BitLocker on Windows (recommended);\n\u2022 Use strong passwords and appropriate roles (ADMIN / DOCTOR / OPERATOR);\n\u2022 Enable database encryption in the app (optional);\n\u2022 Use encrypted ZIP backup and store the password securely.")
B.RG=new A.K("6. Contact","Technical questions about the product: suporte@perfectgestdev.com\nLGPD requests regarding clinical data: contact the clinic (controller).")
B.a2B=s([B.TB,B.S8,B.RK,B.TP,B.Ur,B.RG],t.h)
