B.Tl=new A.K("Introduction","Last updated: July 2026\nPerfectGest I provides clear data control under Google Play and Brazil\u2019s LGPD. The app is local-first.")
B.T9=new A.K("Summary","Client and financial data are not sent automatically to PerfectGest servers. They leave the phone only if you share PDFs, exported backup files, business card PNG/vCard, or show a QR with professional contacts.")
B.S9=new A.K("1. Local management data","Stored in SQLite on the device: clients, commercial estimates, fiscal quotes and fiscal codes, cash, work orders, company data (including logo), business-card snapshot, fiscal reminders.\n\nHow to delete\n\n- In the app: Settings \u2192 Data on this device \u2192 Delete all data on this device\n- Android: Settings \u2192 Apps \u2192 PerfectGest I \u2192 Storage \u2192 Clear data\n- Uninstall the app\n\nWarning: without an external copy, there is no recovery \u2014 we do not keep copies on our servers.\n\nShared backups: delete them manually where you saved them (WhatsApp, email, cloud).")
B.SO=new A.K("2. Firebase / telemetry","Anonymous installation metadata and usage metrics (subscription eligibility / anti-abuse; first business-card save). We do not host card content or logos on servers.\n\nEmail: suporte@perfectgestdev.com \u2014 Subject: Technical Data Deletion Request")
B.SE=new A.K("3. Local notifications","Cancelled when you uninstall or wipe app data.")
B.Sa=new A.K("4. Timelines","Local data: immediate. Firebase telemetry: up to 15 business days after an email request.")
