B.RR=new A.K("Introduction","Last updated: July 2026")
B.T3=new A.K("1. Purpose","These Terms govern PerfectGest I (customers, commercial budgets, fiscal quotes on the Quote/NF-e/NFS-e tab \u2014 local support documents only; no electronic NF-e/NFS-e issuance, cash, work orders, fiscal reminders, digital business card), with data primarily on your device.\n\nClient and financial data stay on the device and are not transmitted automatically. They may leave only through your actions (share PDF, exported backup, business card PNG/vCard/QR). See Privacy Policy.\n\nPublisher: Marcos Leandro dos Santos.")
B.Sr=new A.K("2. Eligibility","Users aged 18 or over.")
B.Tm=new A.K("3. Explore mode, Pro Plan, and subscriptions","- After download: you may explore the app (browse and view the interface) without a subscription.\n- Operations (creating records, generating management PDFs, encrypted backup restore, and other gated actions) require Pro Plan. Without a subscription, the app shows a notice with the plan (reference R$ 9.90/month; official price on Google Play) and the options Subscribe or Continue exploring app features.\n- Pro Plan: unlimited use of active features, encrypted backup restore, and interactive business card in the app \u2014 monthly or annual subscription via Google Play (price and terms in the store).\n- Auto-renewal until cancelled in the Play Store: Payments & subscriptions \u2192 Subscriptions.")
B.TD=new A.K("4. Cancellation","Google Play Store \u2192 Payments & subscriptions.")
B.SX=new A.K("5. Statutory rights (Brazil)","Brazil\u2019s Consumer Code may grant a 7-day withdrawal right where applicable. Refunds via Google Play rules and channels.")
B.SQ=new A.K("6. Fiscal reminders and fiscal quotes","Informational / support only; not tax advice and not official electronic invoice issuance. User responsibility.")
B.TV=new A.K("7. Limitation of liability","Management tool; user responsible for business decisions.")
B.Sb=new A.K("8. Intellectual property","Revocable license; no unlawful reverse engineering.")
B.SS=new A.K("9. Changes","Current version at URL below.")
B.Tv=new A.K("10. Governing law","Brazil; venue Caxias do Sul/RS.")
B.UG=new A.K("11. Contact","suporte@perfectgestdev.com")
